{"tid":14891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支那學野]印度戲院開場前必須播國歌及起立","createTime":"2016-11-30T16:47:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-03T07:23:19.000Z","uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f54cdcc684e9a51cf3977ed23f692cdd8583d61d","tid":14891,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T16:47:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.timesofindia.com/india/Supreme-Court-says-playing-national-anthem-mandatory-in-cinema-halls/articleshow/55701366.cms?utm_source=facebook.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=TOI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Findia%2FSupreme-Court-says-playing-national-anthem-mandatory-in-cinema-halls%2Farticleshow%2F55701366.cms%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook.com%26utm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_campaign%3DTOI&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=50ef4618\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.timesofindia.com/india/Supreme-Court-says-playing-national-anthem-mandatory-in-cinema-halls/articleshow/55701366.cms?utm_source=facebook.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=TOI</a><br />\n<br />\n本來印度既戲院都會自行係開場前播國歌睇國旗，但依家印度最高法院正式下令，規定印度所有戲院播戲前必須先播國歌，觀眾要起立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n支那港共幾時學咖哩玩呢套<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同場加映：<br />\n一個跛腳要坐輪椅既運動員，開場前播國歌時無起立所以俾人打<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.newscrunch.in/2016/10/wheel-chair-bound-activist-salil-chaturvedi-kicked-panaji-theatre-not-standing-national\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newscrunch.in%2F2016%2F10%2Fwheel-chair-bound-activist-salil-chaturvedi-kicked-panaji-theatre-not-standing-national&d=OqNKNX3jJWm7Bjx4wMOex5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=d36a51a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.newscrunch.in/2016/10/wheel-chair-bound-activist-salil-chaturvedi-kicked-panaji-theatre-not-standing-national</a>"},{"pid":"b91904c654ff1af743709dc59daa55abaf7d7219","tid":14891,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"